    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The hemolysis model form is supported by a comprehensive systematic literature review spanning 14 peer-reviewed publications, and discretization error is within the required threshold. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the credibility plan. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
